      </article>
      <article class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-number">s%</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Success Rate</span>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="blog-posts">
    <h2 class="section-title">Latest Articles</h2>
    <div class="posts-grid">
      <article class="blog-post">
        <header class="post-header">
          <h3>Why Businesses Are Embracing Remote Freelancers</h3>
          <div class="post-meta">
            <time datetime="2025-05-18">May 18, 2025</time>
            <span class="category">Industry Trends</span>
          </div>
        </header>
        <section class="post-content">
          <p>Companies worldwide are discovering the benefits of working with remote freelancers. From cost savings to access to global talent, the advantages are compelling.</p>
          <a href="#" class="post-link">Read More</a>
        </section>
      </article>

      <article class="blog-post">
        <header class="post-header">
          <h3>Top 10 Skills in High Demand for Freelancers</h3>
          <div class="post-meta">
            <time datetime="2025-05-15">May 15, 2025</time>
            <span class="category">Career Tips</span>
          </div>
        </header>
        <section class="post-content">
          <p>Discover which skills are most sought after by clients and how you can position yourself for success in the competitive freelancing market.</p>
          <a href="#" class="post-link">Read More</a>
        </section>
      </article>

      <article class="blog-post">
        <header class="post-header">
          <h3>How to Set Your Freelance Rates: A Complete Guide</h3>
          <div class="post-meta">
            <time datetime="2025-05-12">May 12, 2025</time>
            <span class="category">Freelancer Guide</span>
