          <h3>Building Long-term Client Relationships</h3>
          <div class="post-meta">
            <time datetime="2025-05-10">May 10, 2025</time>
            <span class="category">Client Relations</span>
          </div>
        </header>
        <section class="post-content">
          <p>Successful freelancers know that repeat clients are the key to sustainable income. Learn how to nurture lasting professional relationships.</p>
          <a href="#" class="post-link">Read More</a>
