        <header class="post-header">
          <h3>Platform Update: New Features for Better Collaboration</h3>
          <div class="post-meta">
            <time datetime="2025-05-08">May 8, 2025</time>
            <span class="category">Platform News</span>
          </div>
        </header>
        <section class="post-content">
          <p>We've launched new collaboration tools to make project management easier for both freelancers and clients. Here's what's new.</p>
          <a href="#" class="post-link">Read More</a>
        </section>
      </article>

      <article class="blog-post">
        <header class="post-header">
          <h3>The Psychology of Successful Freelancing</h3>
          <div class="post-meta">
